Introduction

Zoe is an Italian singer and lyricist under HOMe. She is a member of the girl group Geenius and a former member of the trainee team Polaris Junior. She is known for participating in JTBC and YG's reality survival show MIXNINE.

Her parents are both Korean but she was born and raised in Lombardy, Italy.
